"""
        Test that an EncryptionKeyInformation struct can be built from a
        dictionary.
        """
client = ProxyKmipClient()
result = client._build_encryption_key_information(None)
self.assertEqual(None, result)
result = client._build_encryption_key_information({'unique_identifier':
    'test', 'cryptographic_parameters': {'block_cipher_mode': enums.
    BlockCipherMode.CBC}})
self.assertIsInstance(result, obj.EncryptionKeyInformation)
self.assertEqual('test', result.unique_identifier)
self.assertIsInstance(result.cryptographic_parameters, obj.
    CryptographicParameters)
self.assertEqual(enums.BlockCipherMode.CBC, result.cryptographic_parameters
    .block_cipher_mode)
